snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
snippet.description:
New game drops! Developers! More!

Minecraft LIVE is our own super special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! 

Weâ€™re updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more! 

After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

American Sign Language: https://www.youtube.com/live/W3uQA_unm0I
British Sign Language: https://youtube.com/live/ZygMYm2sx5U
Audio Descriptions: https://youtube.com/live/DoXrLv__PAY

Check out Minecraft.net for more information!  
https://www.minecraft.net/

id.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
id.description:
Perilisan game baru! Pengembang! Lainnya!

Minecraft LIVE adalah acara super spesial kami yang memberikan Anda info terkini tentang segala hal yang terjadi di dunia Minecraft! Acara berikutnya akan disiarkan pada tanggal 28 September pukul 00.00 WIB.  

Kami memperbarui Minecraft vanilla dengan beberapa peluncuran game per tahun, jadi sekarang kami menyelenggarakan dua acara ini untuk membahas semua fitur baru. Setiap episodenya berisi info terbaru dari pengembang kami, informasi terkini tentang game mendatang yang belum diumumkan, dan lainnya! 

Setelah siaran, nantikan After Show Pembahasan Mendalam saat para pengembang dan tamu kami memamerkan fitur-fitur baru, yang sering kali mengakibatkan kekacauan. Vu Bui akan kembali sebagai pembawa acara dan berusaha memastikan semuanya berjalan lancar. Semoga beruntung untuk orang itu!

ms.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
ms.description:
Pelancaran Permainan Baharu Pembangun! Lagi!

Minecraft LIVE merupakan rancangan khas kami yang memberikan anda maklumat terkini dan menarik mengenai semua yang berlaku dalam dunia Minecraft! Siaran berikutnya akan disiarkan pada 28 September, jam 12 pagi MYT.  

Kami mengemas kini permainan Minecraft Vanilla dengan beberapa keluaran setiap tahun, jadi kini kami menganjurkan dua acara khas untuk memperkenalkan semua ciri baharu. Setiap episod menampilkan maklumat terkini daripada pembangun-pembangun kami, pendedahan eksklusif tentang pelancaran permainan yang belum diumumkan, dan banyak lagi! 

Selepas siaran berakhir, nantikan Deep Dig After Show di mana pembangun serta tetamu kami akan memperkenalkan ciri baharu, yang kadangkala membawa kepada suasana kecoh. Vu Bui akan kembali sebagai pengacara dan berusaha memastikan segalanya berjalan lancar. Semoga dia berjaya!

How I "DIED" on a Hardcore Minecraft SMP

inspired by @4CVIT's naked and afraid series!

thank you to:  @Boosfer @loppezz @FlameFragsMC eggchan @LettuceK @Twirps as well as all of the capital city guards and merchant city players!

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of my music is by AZALI so check him out!)
https://www.youtube.com/@nombra101 (song during the first flame fight!)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

snippet.title: BELLES VILLAIN SONG (Pt 2) - Reclaim My Story | Official Animatic Video | by Lydia the Bard & Frost
snippet.description:
BELLES VILLAIN SONG (Part 2) - Reclaim my Story | Official Animatic Music Video | By Lydia the Bard and Frostudio Chambersonic

STREAM SONG HERE - https://ffm.to/bellepart2
PRESAVE MY DEBUT ALBUM - https://ffm.to/thewoodsdebutalbum.OYD
WATCH PART 1 - https://youtu.be/xFByIo6nujM?si=oM01ONNnR-3IXosb

Itâ€™s the last Villain song for a little while now! (Donâ€™t worry theyâ€™ll be back) I hope you enjoy this extension to Belles story! It felt like Gaston for sure needed dealing with after the last one! Following this release the next thing Iâ€™ll be posting is my album AAAHH

If you dont already know Iâ€™m releasing my debut album â€˜The Woodsâ€™ on October 11th!! SO EXCITED I CANT EVEN BEGIN TO SAY HOW EXCITED I AM FOR YOU TO HEAR IT AAAHAHAHAH. You can presave here - https://ffm.to/thewoodsdebutalbum.OYDhttps:/ Also I hope you enjoyed the conclusion to Figs restaurant dream story aswell!! I think Iâ€™ll open him a restaurant either way. Now enough waffle, the story!

BELLES VILLAIN STORY 

Belle was always the odd one out, the outcast, the outsider. Her whole life she put up with those in her village making fun of her and her Father, so she stayed hidden behind her books. Biding her time. Waiting for the right moment.

That time finally arrived when she was kidnapped by the beast, just another man trying to control her, to tame her. Sheâ€™d put up with that from Gaston for years and so another man mistreating her was nothing new. The beast found that out very quickly. Belle didnâ€™t allow herself to fall in love with him, only let the beast think that. And when her time finally claim she plucked every last petal off that rose and watched as he became a Beast forever. You might question, why, if the beast was now a monster, did he not then attack Belle? Well, that wouldâ€™ve happened, but Belle wasnâ€™t just anyone, Belle had the blood of the women who cast that curse running through her veins. Belle was the enchantresses daughter. 

Now with a Beast ready to attack anyone she willed Belle sets her sights on the town, on Gaston, on her father. Those who run her mother out of the village, the man who tried to force himself upon her, and her father, who was too distracted making his inventions to intervene. Belle has always known she was superior to them, well now it was time to show them just how superior she was. Sheâ€™ll have her revenge, and then sheâ€™ll take her rightful place, as their new God. 

LYRICS

Gosh it disturbs me to see you Gaston
My you look so gaunt
Much has changed since our last meeting Gaston
Iâ€™m no longer a debutante
That monster you were so scared about
Heâ€™s my ally now
Only monster left that I can see around
Stands in front of this crowd

You mocked and harassed
And made pass after pass
And when that didnâ€™t work you planned forceful attacks
So letâ€™s end this fantasy 
Write a new tragedy
And sweetheart
You donâ€™t last the first act

Ill reclaim my story
Take back the end youâ€™ve been hoarding
Delicate words are boring
Tear those pages out-law vain glory
Strike through the cruel and the haughty
I have the pen and authority
Im the author now

But Iâ€™d be remiss to pin this all on you
How could I forget
All these friendly faces, step out, join us too
Come up and meet my new pet
Hold out your hand I swear he wonâ€™t bite
Unless I say so
Come to think it didnâ€™t you all stand aside
When we needed you most

Iâ€™ll remake my past
Change the lines Iâ€™ll recast
As the actors are fired and beats are rehashed
Im done with collaborative
I run the narrative
And my word is fact

Ill reclaim my story
Take back the end youâ€™ve been hoarding
Delicate words are boring
Tear those pages out-law vain glory
Strike through the cruel and the haughty
I have the pen and authority
Im the author now

Patient as I watched you drag behind
Throwing hate cos I had the sharper mind
Jealous words are easy to undermine
Wanna be me? Maybe read a book sometime
While you go write your name in the sand
Im charting stars and Im writing psalms
Even Gods above seem to understand
Iâ€™ll hold this whole world in my hand
So save yourself and accept defeat
Your tale is done now go take a seat
And watch and maybe youâ€™ll learn something
Donâ€™t judge a songbird till she sings
You want me squashed just to save your pride
But I gotta thank you for all the lies
Cos now I finally realise

I am the God your Gods left behind

Ill claim my story
Take back my story
Ill do as you taught me
Iâ€™ll claim my story
Now!


âœ¨CREDITSâœ¨

Vocals / Lyrics - Lydia the Bard 

Music - â€‹â @FrostudioChambersonic 

Animatic - â€ªLuck Buggy - https://www.instagram.com/luck.buggy?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==

Ending ad
Instrumental - Ben Tomalin 
Animatic - Zobeebop - https://www.instagram.com/zobeebop?igsh=MWVxZ3RsaDN2enBjaA==
Fig voice - Alex Runicles

Meliputi Teaser James Gunn untuk Superman 2: Man of Tomorrow, Penebusan Lex Luthor. Kostum Lexo, Akhir Peacemaker Musim 2 Episode 8, Akhir Man of Tomorrow.

Trailer Peacemaker Musim 2 Episode 7. Penjelasan Evil Justice League, Superman, Justice Gang. Akibat Peacemaker Musim 2 Episode 6. Adegan Cameo Lex Luthor di Superman, Krisis The Flash di Bumi X. Kekuatan Eagly, Penjelasan Akhir, Penjelasan Pintu Multiverse, Penjelasan Rick Flag, Penjelasan Kanon Suicide Squad. Enchantress, Joker, Perubahan Batman Ben Affleck, Harley Quinn, Penjelasan Akhir, Adegan Pasca Kredit. Kilas Balik Superman, Penjelasan Referensi Batman dan Gotham City. Justice Gang, Superman, Justice League Berubah ke musim 1 dengan Adegan Flash & Aquaman, Green Lantern, Hawkgirl, Maxwell Lord. Lelucon dan referensi DCEU untuk reboot DCU dari Multiverse Crossover. Trailer Peacemaker Musim 2 Episode 5.

Easter Egg Superman. Penjelasan Justice League baru James Gunn. Fortress Of Solitude, Adegan Cameo Bradley Cooper Jor-El, Robot Kelex, Adegan Baru. Perubahan Batman Baru dan Rencana Film DC untuk Batman Dijelaskan. Rekaman dan Adegan Baru. Fortress of Solitude. Superman vs Ultraman, Evil Superman. Tampilan Pertama Green Lantern. Adegan Mr Terrific Krypto. Superman vs Lex Luthor, Rekaman Baru, Teaser Superman Legacy 2025. Kostum Superman Baru, Penjelasan The Flash Returns. Milly Alcock Supergirl. Supergirl Baru vs Versi Sebelumnya. Teaser Film Supergirl Woman of Tomorrow. David Corenswet Superman, Nicholas Hoult Lex Luthor Dijelaskan, perubahan dari versi Lex Luthor sebelumnya seperti Man of Steel, Batman v Superman, Justice League. The Authority. Alur dan Cerita Superman Legacy Dijelaskan. Penjelasan Supergirl Baru.

Teaser Batman Brave and the Bold dan Batman Baru akan diumumkan tahun depan. Teaser Batman Brave and the Bold dan Batman Baru akan diumumkan tahun depan. Nathan Fillion Green Lantern, Hawkgirl, Mr. Terrific, dan lebih banyak karakter Justice League baru. Mengapa Justice League Baru lebih didasarkan pada Tim Justice League Animasi.

Batman Brave and the Bold. Banyak lagi Trailer DC dan Marvel yang akan datang: Trailer Superman 2025, Trailer Avengers 5 Doomsday, Trailer Spider-Man Brand New Day & Trailer Superman Supergirl segera hadir!

Video lengkap Peacemaker Musim 2 Episode 7 saya akan diposting Kamis depan!

snippet.description:
Find out more about the Update in the articles below!
ğŸ“° https://supr.cl/Update_Oct25
ğŸ“° https://supr.cl/MergeTactics_Oct25 

X â–º https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram â–º https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok â–º https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook â–º https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

snippet.title: LTA Championship Weekend - Texas | 100T vs VKS
snippet.description:
Split 3 marks the Road to the LTA Championship, starting with an all-new format where our teams will Pick a Fight and choose their opponents to start the split, before the Elimination Phase begins and we're All-Fearless Best of Five's All-the-Time! Every game is on the live patch, and every game counts. Watch Split 3 of the LTA North live to find out which team will conquer the conference, fight against LTA South for the LTA Championship, and earn a berth to Worlds 2025. For more info about Split 3, including format breakdowns and other updates, check out our Split 3 Primer.

Catch the LTA every Saturday and Sunday:
LTA Cross Conference begins at 1PM PT / 3PM MT / 4PM ET / 6PM BT

LTA North teams include Cloud9 Kia, FlyQuest, Team Liquid, Dignitas, Shopify Rebellion, LYON, Disguised, and 100 Thieves.
LTA South teams include Fluxo W7M, Furia, Isurus, Leviatan, LOUD, paiN Gaming, RED Canids Kalunga, and Vivo Keyd Stars.

You can always learn more and view the full match schedule at https://lolesports.com/en-US?leagues=lta_n,lta_s
Follow us:

https://twitter.com/ltanorth
https://instagram.com/ltanorth
https://tiktok.com/@ltanorth
https://discord.gg/LTANorth

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. Itâ€™s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Teman-teman saya: @digitalnex

Apa itu Roblox? ROBLOX adalah taman bermain dan lokakarya virtual daring, tempat anak-anak dari segala usia dapat berinteraksi, berkreasi, bersenang-senang, dan belajar dengan aman. Keunikannya adalah hampir semua hal di ROBLOX dirancang dan dibangun oleh anggota komunitas. ROBLOX dirancang untuk anak usia 13 hingga 18 tahun, tetapi terbuka untuk semua usia. Setiap pemain memulai dengan memilih avatar dan memberinya identitas. Mereka kemudian dapat menjelajahi ROBLOX â€” berinteraksi dengan orang lain melalui obrolan, bermain gim, atau berkolaborasi dalam proyek kreatif. Setiap pemain juga diberikan lahan mereka sendiri yang belum dikembangkan beserta kotak peralatan virtual untuk merancang dan membangun apa pun â€” entah itu gedung pencakar langit yang dapat dilayari, helikopter yang berfungsi, mesin pinball raksasa, gim multipemain "Capture the Flag", atau kreasi lain yang belum terbayangkan. Tidak ada biaya untuk sebidang lahan virtual pertama ini. Dengan berpartisipasi dan membangun hal-hal keren, anggota ROBLOX dapat memperoleh lencana khusus serta dolar ROBLOX ("Robux"). Sebagai imbalannya, mereka dapat berbelanja di katalog daring untuk membeli pakaian dan aksesori avatar serta material bangunan premium, komponen interaktif, dan mekanisme kerja.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. Itâ€™s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Wat is Roblox? ROBLOX is een online virtuele speeltuin en werkplaats waar kinderen van alle leeftijden veilig kunnen interacteren, creÃ«ren, plezier kunnen hebben en leren. Het is uniek omdat vrijwel alles op ROBLOX is ontworpen en gebouwd door leden van de community. ROBLOX is ontworpen voor 13- tot 18-jarigen, maar staat open voor mensen van alle leeftijden. Elke speler begint met het kiezen van een avatar en geeft deze een identiteit. Vervolgens kunnen ze ROBLOX verkennen - door met anderen te communiceren door te chatten, games te spelen of samen te werken aan creatieve projecten. Elke speler krijgt ook een eigen stuk onbebouwd land, samen met een virtuele gereedschapskist waarmee hij alles kan ontwerpen en bouwen â€“ of het nu een bestuurbare wolkenkrabber, een werkende helikopter, een gigantische flipperkast, een multiplayer "Capture the Flag"-spel of een andere, nog te bedenken creatie is. Dit eerste stukje virtueel land is gratis. Door deel te nemen en coole dingen te bouwen, kunnen ROBLOX-leden speciale badges en ROBLOX-dollars ("Robux") verdienen. In ruil daarvoor kunnen ze in de online catalogus avatarkleding en -accessoires kopen, evenals premium bouwmaterialen, interactieve componenten en werkende mechanismen.

His transformation from innocent noob to a unstoppable killing force, how did he end up in that role and what drove him to become a killer. This time I kinda experimented with video format and decided to make video look more of "cinematic-like" or resemble a skit rather then realistic video, let me know what you guys think of this format and if i should continue doing my future videos more cinematic-like.
please - do NOT send hate or harass anyone mentioned in this video, this video is a skit for comedy entertainment purposes and nothing more then that, please like unironically i am here not to hate on ANY groups of people/fandoms/avatar styles, I genuinely respect everyone but this video is just over exaggerated for entertainment purposes. This is Minecraft, but Steve is learning the Sad Story of the DEER! When Steve discovers the Deerâ€™s story tied to a scientists and all the other children, showing the past of the Deer kid. He needs to discover their secrets and mysteries! This is The Sad Story of the DEER in Minecraft...

MORE CHECKPOINT ADVENTURES:

â€£ MINECRAFT DIMENSION: https://bit.ly/3mKfUOL


Â¬

Minecraft is an open world game that has no specific goals for the player to accomplish, allowing players a large amount of freedom in choosing how to play the game however, there is an achievement system. The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objectsâ€”mainly cubesâ€”that are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

#Checkpoint #Minecraft

snippet.title: How to Beat DARK SOULS 1 With Only Spears
snippet.description:
Criminally underrated, the spears in Dark Souls are actually surprisingly good.
With lots of variation and unique mechanics, I'm confused why they don't get more love.
Can you beat Dark Souls 1 with only spears? Absolutely.
Now let's talk about the best way to do it.

|| SHOUTOUTS ||
@OGSckorpiion for their video on how to skip the Asylum Demon.
Take that, semantics!

snippet.title: ULTRAKILL 94 - Deathcatcher
snippet.description:
Deathcatchers are a rare enemy that causes all nearby dead foes to get resurrected until it's destroyed.
The resurrected versions are slightly slower and weaker, but as the dead stack up, their numbers can easily become overwhelming.

snippet.title: My Starter Base Can Kill Anyone
snippet.description:
Join the server - IP: Lifesteal.Net
Bedrock Server IP - bedrock.lifesteal.net
Bedrock Server Port - 19132

Lifesteal Net's new season had just begun and instead of gaining power and glory, I was getting spawn camped... over and over. Set back to nothing, I vowed to make a change, to end the cycle of the abuse towards me by trapping the spawn campers who so very much wanted to kill me. In order to do so...... I turned a starter base into a trap which killed over 50 players.

wanna join my discord?
https://www.youtube.com/reddoons/join

get me lunar cape:
https://lunarclient.com/reddoons
use code "RED"

Edited by @Flordo 
Thumbnail by @BursstyPlays

en.description:
Join the server - IP: Lifesteal.Net
Bedrock Server IP - bedrock.lifesteal.net

Lifesteal Net's new season had just begun and instead of gaining power and glory, I was getting spawn camped... over and over. Set back to nothing, I vowed to make a change, to end the cycle of the abuse towards me by trapping the spawn campers who so very much wanted to kill me. In order to do so...... id.title: Menguji Slot Huff Nâ€™ Puff Baru!
id.description:
Saya akan membagikan $50.000 yang PASTI Anda TIDAK ingin melewatkannya!: http://codebrettski.com

Kami KEMBALI di Kasino, dan saya sedang menguji mesin slot huff nâ€™ puff "Weâ€™ve Had Enuff" yang baru! Tanpa spoiler... tapi vlog ini akan menarik. Terima kasih semuanya sudah menonton! Kalian semua cantik, dan saya sangat menghargai kalian semua yang telah ikut serta dalam perjalanan gila ini. Doakan saya beruntung, dan sampai jumpa di vlog berikutnya! Ayo berperang.

Brettski berjalan memasuki hiruk pikuk Kasino Golden Peak yang berkilauan dengan angkuh, mengenakan kacamata hitam, dan kamera menyala. Ribuan dolar di sakunya, baterai baru di GoPro, dan satu misi: menaklukkan slot *Huff N Puff: Weâ€™ve Had Enuff* yang baru. Kabarnya, mesin itu mudah berubah â€” seperti, *menghancurkan-rumah-Anda* mudah berubah.

Dia menemukannya di sudut, bersinar seperti jebakan. "Ayo kita ambil uang ini," bisiknya, sambil memasukkan voucher $1.000 yang masih baru.

Putaran pertama: nihil. Kedua: teaser. Ketiga? Ronde bonus. Babi-babi memekik, helm beterbangan, dan Serigala Jahat Besar muncul... mengenakan rantai emas dan kacamata hitam. "Dia seperti aku jika aku furry," tawa Brettski.

Laluâ€”*BOOM*. Uang $4.200 berhasil. Brettski menjerit. Dia menari. Kamera bergetar.

Tapi mesinnya belum selesai.

Beberapa menit kemudian: bonus lagi. Lalu yang ketiga. Dia tak boleh kalah. Mesin itu mencetak tiket $12.000. Dia menyebutnya *Mode Huff Daddy*. Penonton di obrolan siaran langsung meledak. "Bayar!" pinta mereka.

Tapi Brettski menggandakannya.

Dia memasukkan setengahnya lagi, mengejar *Bonus Mega Huff* yang mistis â€” yang dibisikkan di forum, konon bisa dibuka dengan menyusun enam helm emas sambil memegang babi platinum.

Putaran demi putaran. $500 hilang. Lalu $1.000.

Akhirnya â€” *KLIK*. Enam helm. Satu babi platinum.

Layarnya bermasalah.

Mesinnya macet.

Lalu di-boot ulangâ€¦ ke *MODE ADMIN*.

Keamanan bergegas menghampiri. "Pak, kami ingin Anda menjauh dari mesin ini."

"Tapi saya yang memicu bonusnya! Babi platinum! Saya merekamnya!"

Seorang manajer muncul, pucat. Dia menatap rekaman itu. Lalu mencondongkan tubuhnya.

"Anda seharusnya tidak menekan tombol itu. Versi permainan itu belumâ€¦ dirilis secara resmi."

Senyum Brettski memudar.

"Apa maksud Anda 'belum dirilis'?"

Manajer itu melihat sekeliling dengan gugup.

"Pakâ€¦ siapa yang memberi tahu Anda mesin ini ada di sini?"

**BERSAMBUNG.**

Siapakah Brettski? Brettski adalah seorang Penjudi Profesional, mirip dengan legenda kuno Vegas Matt, Bluff, DegenDalt, TheBigJackpot, atau Lady Luck HQ! Namun, tidak seperti legenda-legenda ini, Brettski memiliki pengetahuan kuno yang tersimpan selama ribuan tahun yang digali oleh para tetua, dalam keterampilan seperti Mesin Slot, Roulette, Blackjack, Craps, Bubble Craps, Poker, dan Bakarat. Tujuan Brettski sebagai Penjudi Profesional sederhana: menguasai seluruh Las Vegas, menggunakan dana yang diperoleh dari Perjudian. Berlanggananlah untuk mendukung perjalanannya dalam mendominasi dunia.

snippet.title: 8 Pro Speedrunners vs 1 Secret Cheater
snippet.description:
I've gathered 9 pro speedrunners to race against eachother, but one is secretly cheating in creative mode. Can the pros figure out who is cheating, or will the imposter be able to Craft A Lie?

CREDITS:
Editing: @biggestbee 

Players:
Aquacorde: @Aquacorde https://twitch.tv/aquacordeMC
Automatt: @AutomattPL https://twitch.tv/AutomattPL
Mongey: @bigbigmongey https://www.twitch.tv/bigbigmongey
Doogile: @Doogile https://www.twitch.tv/doogile
Erik: @Erikfzf https://www.twitch.tv/erikfzf
Feinberg: @FeinbergMC https://www.twitch.tv/feinberg
Hax: @hackingnoises https://www.twitch.tv/hackingnoisess
Infume: @infumemc https://www.twitch.tv/infume
Silverr: @silverrruns https://www.twitch.tv/silverrruns

My Twitch: 
https://twitch.tv/nerdi

POST MATCH DISCUSSION:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJOqZ0N6hew

Music from Silksong/Hollow Knight OSTs & Epidemic Sound

RULES:
9 players will all be in a private Ranked lobby. Each round, the slowest player to complete the seed is eliminated*. Secretly, one of the 9 is going to be in creative mode (the imposter) for every round. They will have an additional side task each new round (e.g. place 64 diamond blocks) that they must complete before entering the end fountain. After a seed is played, the remaining players will discuss the seed for 3 minutes and choose to either vote out a player or pass. The player with the most votes will be eliminated; if it is a tie, then no players will be eliminated. If the runners vote out the imposter, they win. If the imposter survives until there is only 1 other runner left, then they win. 

*There will also be a time limit (15min), so if several runners do not finish the seed, the runner further behind in the splits will be eliminated. If there are several runners stuck in the same split, one will randomly be eliminated; this rule will also be applied to the creative mode runner if they do not finish the seed.

Some additional things:
-Advancements will be on for all players. So the imposter must be careful about doing things too quickly or obtaining random advancements.

-The creative mode runner is not allowed to use commands or the extra saved hotbars.

-The creative mode runner may choose not to complete the seed, but get far enough into it that they are not eliminated if they notice several runners dying. So, if you see a player not finish a seed, they could still be the imposter.
